5314280/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0520271440&linkCode=as2&tag=teco06-20","position":null,"is_pdf":false,"eyebrow":null},{"label":"READ_Book","headline":"The Lost Whale: The True Story of an Orca Named Luna","blurb":"","note":"Michael Parfit and Suzanne Chisholm\r\nSt. Martin's Press, 2013","link_url":"http://www.amazon.com/Lost-Whale-True-Story-Named/dp/0312353642/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0520271440&linkCode=as2&tag=teco06-20","position":null,"is_pdf":false,"eyebrow":null},{"label":"READ_Book","headline":"The Dusky Dolphin: Master Acrobat Off Different Shores","blurb":"In particular, the chapter \"A Large-Brained Social Mammal\"","note":"Bernd Wursig and Melany Wursig\r\nAcademic Press, 2009","link_url":"http://www.amazon.com/Dusky-Dolphin-Master-Acrobat-Different/dp/0123737230/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0520271440&linkCode=as2&tag=teco06-20","position":null,"is_pdf":false,"eyebrow":null},{"label":"READ_Book","headline":"Coming of Age With Elephants: A Memoir","blurb":"","note":"Joyce Poole\r\nHyperion, 1997","link_url":"http://www.amazon.com/Coming-Age-Elephants-Joyce-Poole/dp/0786881917/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0520271440&linkCode=as2&tag=teco06-20","position":null,"is_pdf":false,"eyebrow":null},{"label":"READ_Book","headline":"The Dolphin in the Mirror: Exploring Dolphin Minds and Saving Dolphin Lives","blurb":"","note":"Diana Reiss\r\nMariner Books, 2012","link_url":"http://www.amazon.com/Dolphin-Mirror-Exploring-Minds-Saving/dp/0547844611/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0520271440&linkCode=as2&tag=teco06-20","position":null,"is_pdf":false,"eyebrow":null},{"label":"READ_Book","headline":"Decade of the Wolf: Returning The Wild To Yellowstone","blurb":"","note":"Douglas Smith and Gary Ferguson\r\nLyons Press, 2012","link_url":"http://www.amazon.com/Decade-Wolf-Revised-Updated-Yellowstone/dp/076277